  "Category": "Developer Tools",
  "Title": "uTPro Audit Log Viewer",
  "Description": "Audit log & content log viewer for the Umbraco backoffice (Umbraco 16, 17, 18). Browse, search, filter, sort and export the umbracoAudit and umbracoLog tables from the Settings section - without writing any SQL. Includes a unified Timeline merging audit and content logs, a Content Logs view, and an Audit Trail, with full-text search, user and date filters, quick date ranges (This month, last 30/7 days, today, custom), sortable columns, quick edit links to documents and media, a GMT/UTC time toggle, server-side paging, CSV export, and shareable/bookmarkable URL filters. Read-only and safe (no database schema changes), works on SQL Server and SQLite. Perfect for content auditing, user activity tracking, debugging, security review and compliance/GDPR reporting.",
